query:
INSERT INTO album (
                "title",
                "lidarr_id",
                "musicbrainz_id",
                "artist_id"
            ) VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3,
                (SELECT id FROM artist WHERE lidarr_id = $4)
            ) ON CONFLICT(lidarr_id) DO UPDATE SET
                "title" = $1,
                "musicbrainz_id" = $3
            RETURNING "id"
